snippet.title: Fabric - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Store Page Available: http://store.steampowered.com/app/489660/

Fabric is a First Person Puzzle Game with bending and squeezing mechanic to solve the challenging puzzles and complete the glitchy voxel-based levels.
